race.comment: FLUENT (11) resumes. Her form last time in reads well for this having been around the mark in some good 3yo races over the Autumn, including a narrow fifth in a G2 race in Adelaide behind Reserve Bank, who went on to win the G1 Goodwood next time out. Sets up well here and can return a winner. STEEL MOVE (10) has been right around the mark in three runs back from a spell although is becoming quite frustrating having been turned over at short odds his past two. No surprise if he made amends. INNOCENT ENUFF (7) is racing well. She's found one better her past three and sets up nicely from the gate. SEA POEM (8) can bounce back off a slightly disappointing run last time.
